titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on Mixtures of 1-[[bis(4-fluorophenyl)methylsiyl]methyl]-1H-1,2,4-triazole with xylene and inert application adjuvants.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 10/30/2009--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend temporarily the duty on Mixtures of 1-[[bis(4-fluorophenyl)methylsiyl]methyl]-1H-1,2,4-triazole with xylene and inert application adjuvants.
